From: Jakub Jirutka <jakub@jirutka.cz>
Date: Tue, 09 Jun 2026 15:43:10 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Relax version constraints so we can use system packages

...and also add qh3 to explicit dependencies to fix HTTP/3 tests failing
on arm*, loongarch64. It'd be better to avoid qh3 completely, but this
would require patching niquests.

diff --git a/tests/requirements.txt b/tests/requirements.txt
index d27c6b1..024173c 100644
--- a/tests/requirements.txt
+++ b/tests/requirements.txt
@@ -1,6 +1,7 @@
-pytest~=8.3
+pytest>=8.3
 jinja2~=3.1
-pyopenssl~=24.3
+pyopenssl>=24.3
 niquests~=3.11
+qh3~=1.7
 grpcio~=1.68
 opentelemetry-proto~=1.28
